## âœ… Directory Structure Highlights
- `ios/Flutter/Release.xcconfig` â€“ Custom overrides for Release builds
- `ios/Flutter/Debug.xcconfig` â€“ Custom overrides for Debug builds
- `pubspec.yaml` â€“ Only declares Firebase REST + Firestore
